  <brief_title>Steroid Injection vs. BioDRestore for Patients With Knee OA</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Double-blind, Randomized Study Comparing Steroid Injection and BioDRestore for Patients With Knee Osteoarthritis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
